00:14:07,339 --> 00:14:10,420
unless it's her story, in which case you don't necessarily understand the story anyway,

223
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,761
but that's okay, it fits the genre.

224
00:14:12,261 --> 00:14:18,665
I mean, we've all heard Obra Dinn described as narrative Sudoku, okay?

