00:14:19,025 --> 00:14:21,626
But the thing about Sudoku is that when you're doing a Sudoku,

226
00:14:21,646 --> 00:14:24,808
there's that end bit, which this is a picture of the end bit of a Sudoku,

227
00:14:24,828 --> 00:14:26,709
where you're really just putting numbers in.

228
00:14:27,089 --> 00:14:28,470
You're not actually doing anything.

229
00:14:29,450 --> 00:14:35,075
you totally could just stop at that point because like in any meaningful sense the sudoku puzzle

