547
00:33:09,645 --> 00:33:15,289
So the whole game rests on the implementation of this accusation scene, of this constructed argument.

548
00:33:16,310 --> 00:33:19,492
So we approached that by building it in the most straightforward way that we possibly could,

549
00:33:20,173 --> 00:33:26,998
mainly so that it could grow barnacles and sidetracks and subcontent as we playtested it and developed the game.

