00:33:41,536 --> 00:33:43,137
I think yarn spinner has something similar,

555
00:33:43,157 --> 00:33:44,798
but the idea is it starts at the top

556
00:33:45,018 --> 00:33:46,459
and it drops through content

557
00:33:46,519 --> 00:33:47,759
and it always reaches the bottom.

558
00:33:48,139 --> 00:33:49,460
And there might be choices and branching,

559
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:51,681
but it's guaranteed to hit that final beat.

560
00:33:52,601 --> 00:33:54,122
The idea there is we want to make sure

561
00:33:54,162 --> 00:33:56,623
that whatever happens, we definitely reach a conclusion.

