00:35:48,107 --> 00:35:52,429
happens, the drop-down idea again, we will eventually reach a conclusion and some kind

603
00:35:52,470 --> 00:35:57,273
of outcome that's accepted by the whole group. It's considered now to be definitively true,

604
00:35:58,534 --> 00:35:59,178
this topic.

605
00:36:00,030 --> 00:36:07,194
causes this conclusion here. And that conclusion will accumulate against somebody. It'll be some

