00:36:19,821 --> 00:36:25,164
slept in. So that means everybody concludes that Veronica is lying. And that's a black mark against

610
00:36:25,304 --> 00:36:29,606
Veronica. It goes in her ledger and it's one point against her.

611
00:36:31,645 --> 00:36:32,945
So that's, we do that for each topic.

