00:50:50,395 --> 00:50:55,898
you choose to go with the set dressing of a visual novel and would you have chosen a

862
00:50:55,958 --> 00:50:59,780
different kind of format if you were going to make it again?

863
00:50:59,800 --> 00:50:59,841
So

864
00:51:04,532 --> 00:51:10,135
I have a kind of honest answer, which I feel like I ought to say, which is we made it the way we did

865
00:51:10,195 --> 00:51:14,596
because we really did try to make this game as fast as possible because we were supposed to be

866
00:51:14,636 --> 00:51:19,498
working on our Highland game and like we kind of did this for fun. So the format we took was because

867
00:51:19,518 --> 00:51:24,060
it was very easy to implement and to understand from a design point of view. We saw like the

868
00:51:24,080 --> 00:51:27,561
classic visual novel there, we were like yep we can definitely build that, let's build that.

